ssh 

you can generate ssh keys by
 
 ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "your_email@example.com"
 thats will genearate in .shh a id_rsa.pub and a id_rsa 


rename your public key "id_rsa.pub" to "authorized_keys" and put it in .ssh directory in vicitm machine and now ypu can login wothout password 

